snippet.title: Depper Jar: The test experience - UNDEREVENT 2023 Trailer
snippet.description:
Trailer featured in the UNDEREVENT of 2023:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ansCGZUhtVk

Follow the game here:
https://gamejolt.com/games/1/564312

Music made by Ray "TheRadGuy" Mike:
https://twitter.com/theradguymik
https://soundcloud.com/user-277708053

Artwork of green MC (0:25) made by Cemarmol

The anthology turn-based RPG with fast QTE-based Battles and different game modes that had the chance to appear in the UNDEREVENT 2023!
Honestly I'm still very happy how my game has connected with everyone is the community. Expect many updates to come in the future with even goofier enemies and absurd attacks!
